data.title: Pranjal Chalise Felicitated as Wai Wai Glocal Teen Hero Nepal 2021
data.snippet:
# Pranjal Chalise Felicitated as Wai Wai Glocal Teen Hero Nepal 2021

Nepal News Agency

Shares

Share

Tweet

Share

Kathmandu. Mr. Pranjal Chalise,19 years old Technopreneur from Kathmandu has been awarded the title of ‚ÄúWai Wai Glocal Teen Hero Nepal 2021‚Äù amidst a Virtual Award ceremony organized by Glocal Pvt. Ltd today.

It is the seventh iteration of the Glocal Teen Hero Award, which is the only national platform in Nepal to identify and honor outstanding teenagers whose creativity, commitment, experience, and strong leadership have helped them achieve success in life. [...] Mr. Pranjal was selected among the Top Six Finalists of the competition viz Mr. Anurag Chapagain, (18 years, Youtuber, Nawalparasi); Mr. Deepak Sutihar (19 years, Social Entrepreneur, Saptari); Ms. Khusbu Bhandari, (18 years,Wildlife Conservationist, Chitwan); Ms. Neha Gurung, (19 years, Social Activist, Kathmandu); and Ms. Sabhya Rai, (19 years, Education Activist, IIam)

Mr. Pranjal Chalise has aided the Blind Community by inventing Drishti Nepal, which helps the blind community in currency bills recognition and cash transactions. [...] The three days Glocal International Teen Conference ended successfully with the presence of teenagers from different countries and productive interaction, discussion & inspiring mentorship.

Published on: Sep 01, 2021

Dear Hom Nath Chalise ,

As far as I can see it is (in this case) because the journal where your paper is published in is not properly indexed in Google Scholar.

Furthermore (see print screen) your name is not properly indicated. Not sure when you uploaded your paper here on RG (use academia.edu as well to speed up the process) but sooner or later GS will pick your paper up.

Best regards.
